    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>If you are using this inside Codeigniter, you can use the methods:</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$jobs</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$this</span>-&gt;job_model, <span class="hljs-string">"sortJobs"</span>));  <span class="hljs-comment">// function inside Model</span>
<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$jobs</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">array</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$this</span>, <span class="hljs-string">"sortJobs"</span>)); <span class="hljs-comment">// Written inside Controller.</span>
</code></pre>

<p>@rmooney thank you for the suggestion. It really helps me.</p>
    </div>
