    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Thanks for the inspirations, I also had to add an external $translator parameter</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$listable_products</span>, function(<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>) {
    <span class="hljs-keyword">global</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$translator</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">strcmp</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">getFullTitle</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$translator</span>), <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>-&gt;<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">getFullTitle</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$translator</span>));
});
</code></pre>
    </div>
